unnormalised: Fakt ek yaad divpavpachi gozal mhanllear nagri kaideant, foujdari kaidea bhaxen nhoi, prove korpachi jababdari dava korpeancher asta. Dekhun, zoxem Shri. Sharma-n ek girestkaiechea zhogddeak lagun Rs. 5,00,000 nuksaan zalea mhunn sangta zalear, tannem aplem magnnem prove korpak puravo divpak zai. 1963 chea Specific Relief Act khal ichea kesank zaitim vorsam lagtat. Toxench, limitation periods lagu zatat, sadharanponnan je disak vostu ghodlea tea disasaun 3 vorsam. Odhik mahiti khatir Adv. Patil-ak vicharun gheiat.
normalised: fokot ek yaad divavnni ki deevanni kaideant, foujdari kaidea bhaxen nhoi, sabut dakhovpachi zobabdari vadiacher asta. dekhun, zodd’ddo Mister Sharma ek propertichea ghotalleant rupia panch lakh nuksan bharpai dakholl kortat, tor tannim apli dakhol’li porinnam sid’dh korpak sabut divpak zai. Specific Relief Act, ek hojar nauxim saxtti timi talentlea hea sarkhea kesanim voirsa lagtat. tache xivai, yaad dovrat ki mearyadi kall lagu zatat, sadharonnoponnan karyakaronachi survat zalea uprant tin voirsa. odhik spox̣ṭtate khatir odhivakta Patilachi salah gheiat.
